Private Mat Storage is $10/mo for Monthly Pass holders, $20/mo otherwise
Mat rental is included in the class pricing.
Cancellation less than 6-hrs before the class start time is considered a "late cancel" and the class will be deducted from your account.

Rules & Requests

Time: We have a 5-minute late policy. Arrive early to give yourself time to sign in and change. Don’t stress, but if you are running late, the class may already be full or the door locked. If you are able to enter late, please enter the room quietly without disrupting others. If you need to leave early, tell the teacher before class and follow their guidelines. Please inform the teacher of any emergency situations and come up with a solution together.

Space: Practice awareness when placing your mat down and make space for yourself and others. It helps to stagger the mats so the front of the mats are not lined up. You may need to adjust your mat as more people enter the room to keep a good spacing vibe.

Shoes: Leave them by the studio entrance or put them inside your bag to bring into the practice room. No shoes in the practice room unless bagged!

Stuff: Please store your valuables on the shelves in the yoga room and not by your mat or in the coatroom. No tech use allowed in practice rooms before, during or after class (a.k.a. ever). Please put your phone on silent (not vibrate) and in your bag. We will provide a small charging station by the shelving units and that is the only place you should charge your phone during class.

Thank you for helping us preserve the sacred space of the practice rooms and overall yoga studio vibe.

Thank You

Private Yoga Inquiry

LIVESTREAM FAQs

Livestream FAQs

CAN I USE MY EXISTING MEMBERSHIP OR CLASS CARDS?
Yes.

IF I HAVE A CLASS CARD BUT WANT TO USE ONLINE CLASSES, HOW DO I DO THAT?
Simply purchase “Online Classes” and those classes will be applied to your online classes when you register. $18 for a single class, $80 for a 5 pack, $30 for 3 if you are new to Yogamaya.

HOW FAR IN ADVANCE MUST I REGISTER?
At least 10-min prior to the class start time, the earlier the better.

HOW DO I USE ZOOM?
You can access your ZOOM links from your phone (download the ZOOM app first).
You can access your ZOOM links from your computer. Follow the link it will ask you permission to open the ZOOM app on your computer – say yes to enter the meeting.

WHEN SHOULD I EXPECT TO RECEIVE MY ZOOM LINKS?
You will receive your link at both 15-min & 5-min prior to the exact class start time. If you do not see your link by 5-min before the class start time, check your spam. If you still do not receive the link, email us here.

WHAT IF I LOST TRACK OF TIME AND TRY TO ENTER THE LIVESTREAM LATE?
You will not be able to join the class 5-minutes or more after the class start time.

WHAT IF I HAVE TECH ISSUES?
We highly recommend entering the meeting “waiting room” as soon as you get the links. This will give you time to ensure you have no tech issues.  If you have issues entering the meeting, email us here and will try to assist you.

WILL THE CLASSES BE RECORDED?
No.

AM I REQUIRED TO SHARE MY VIDEO?
No, of course not. But we appreciate & recommend you do! It helps to see bodies moving and your pets.

AM I MUTED?
Yes, all participants are muted upon entry.

LIVESTREAM INFO

Livestream Info

OUR CLASSES ARE NOW LIVESTREAM USING ZOOM MEETING LINKS.

REGISTRATION FOR EACH CLASS CLOSES EXACTLY 10-MIN BEFORE A CLASS-TIME STARTS.
Our reservation system does not permit registration inside the 10-min window before the class start time. If you want to join a 6pm class, you will need to register by 5:49pm at the very latest. You can register at any time in advance of the class.

If you miss the 10-min registration window, our reservation system will tell you there was an error processing your reservation.

WE WILL EMAIL YOU A LINK TO THE YOGAMAYA LIVE STREAM CLASS 15-MIN & 5-MIN BEFORE THE CLASS START TIME.
Follow the link and the prompts to get into the class. If you do not see your link by 5-min before the class start time, check your spam. If you still do not receive the link, email us here.

TAKE THE CLASS AT THE CLASS START TIME.
LIVESTREAM classes start & end on time. No recording of the class will be available after the class.

WE HAVE A 5-MIN LATE POLICY FOR THE LIVESTREAM CLASSES.
If you attempt to enter the class 5-minutes after the class start time, you will not be able to join the class.
